high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave and take the glass out and shut the door of the microwave.
Go right and turn to face the counter to the right of the microwave.
Put the class on the left side of the shelf above the counter.
Pick the knife up from under the tomato on the right.
Put the knife in the glass.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass in a shelf with a knife in it.

high_descs: Make your way to the microwave.
Open the microwave and take the glass out of the microwave, then close the microwave.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the glass on the upper back part of the counter.
Pick up the furthest back butter knife off of the counter.
Put the butter knife in the glass that is on the back part of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a butter knife in a glass on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the refrigerator, to the microwave, above the dishwasher, on your left.
Remove the glass cup from the microwave.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the counter space between the dishwasher and the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the back, lifted counter, to the right of the black coffee cup.
Pick up the knife underneath the tomato on the far right of the lifted counter in the back.
Place the knife from the counter into the glass cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a glass cup.
